   "originalText": "SPECULATIVE  (opt-in: no-tool +\nlexically-clean turn)\nvoice the reply NOW \u2192 run NLI +\nverifier OFF the first-audio path \u2192\nemit a correction only if it fires.\n~0ms perceived latency.\nTRADEOFF: corrected-AFTER, not\nprevented, on those turns.\nTool calls / numbers / commitments\nstay SYNCHRONOUS.",
